- No. It's not good.

968
01:02:04,416 --> 01:02:08,458
It will need the red
of the strawberries

969
01:02:08,666 --> 01:02:11,708
at five in the morning.
You understand me, Armando?

970
01:02:11,916 --> 01:02:15,583
I'd wake up at five in the morning
only when I was a soldier.

971
01:02:15,791 --> 01:02:19,708
And I wouldn't look
at the color of the strawberries!

972
01:02:19,916 --> 01:02:22,791
Gaetanino, tell her something.

973
01:02:23,000 --> 01:02:25,666
I am warming her up.

974
01:02:25,875 --> 01:02:28,333
When the time comes
I will tell her something.

975
01:02:28,541 --> 01:02:32,750
- Listen! Will you talk to her?
- I will try.

976
01:02:32,958 --> 01:02:34,791
But I can't promise.

977
01:02:35,000 --> 01:02:38,875
Today is Sunday, they made lasagne.

978
01:02:39,083 --> 01:02:42,083
You know what happens in these cases.

979
01:02:42,291 --> 01:02:45,916
You are always making up excuses!

980
01:02:46,125 --> 01:02:49,875
The cat to be quick
made blind kittens.

981
01:02:50,083 --> 01:02:53,458
- Do you want to be like the cat?
- No. I want to marry Carmelina!

982
01:02:53,666 --> 01:02:57,791
Don't worry, go home and wait for me.

983
01:02:58,000 --> 01:03:00,000
Take care of the Turkish man.

984
01:03:00,208 --> 01:03:03,708
I don't understand why Amalia
put Sisinella in boarding school.

985
01:03:03,916 --> 01:03:07,000
She says that she needed
a good education

986
01:03:07,208 --> 01:03:09,583
and that she would stay home
doing nothing.

987
01:03:09,791 --> 01:03:12,666
No, this is not the reason.

988
01:03:12,875 --> 01:03:16,625
Since the Turkish man arrived,
everything is crazy in this house.

989
01:03:16,833 --> 01:03:18,291
Here he is.

990
01:03:18,500 --> 01:03:20,750
- Are we eating?
- It's you.

991
01:03:20,958 --> 01:03:23,583
Sit down, lunch will be served soon.

992
01:03:23,791 --> 01:03:26,875
Amalia isn't here yet?

993
01:03:27,083 --> 01:03:29,458
No. Annunziata
will take you company.

994
01:03:29,666 --> 01:03:31,208
What fun!

995
01:03:34,291 --> 01:03:37,208
- I would like to be with you alone.
- With me?

996
01:03:37,416 --> 01:03:42,166
- I would like to talk to you.
- There is nothing to do with me!

997
01:03:43,166 --> 01:03:46,750
What did you understand? I have
to tell you something important.

998
01:03:46,958 --> 01:03:50,583
And so? This is a respectable house.

999
01:03:50,791 --> 01:03:52,791
Do you think this is your harem?

1000
01:03:53,000 --> 01:03:57,291
Excuse me if I am late,
you know how these hairdressers are!

1001
01:03:57,500 --> 01:04:01,875
- Between one lock and another...
- Mom, what did you do?

1002
01:04:02,083 --> 01:04:04,875
You don't like me?

1003
01:04:05,083 --> 01:04:07,291
Don't listen to her.

1004
01:04:07,500 --> 01:04:09,875
You are amazing!

1005
01:04:10,083 --> 01:04:14,708
Let's make a toast
to your wonderful transformation.

1006
01:04:14,916 --> 01:04:18,416
- Thank you.
- I'd prefer poison!

1007
01:04:18,625 --> 01:04:21,750
- What do you mean?
- Don't you mind her.

1008
01:04:21,958 --> 01:04:25,083
She doesn't deserve your kindness.

1009
01:04:25,416 --> 01:04:28,541
I know who is she thinking about!

1010
01:04:28,750 --> 01:04:31,500
Yes, I am thinking
about him. My Nini.

1011
01:04:31,708 --> 01:04:35,625
He is so beautiful
and I am so in love with him.

1012
01:04:35,833 --> 01:04:38,083
Come on dear, don't cry.

1013
01:04:38,291 --> 01:04:40,333
It's a fixation!

1014
01:04:40,541 --> 01:04:43,708
- Nicolino.
- I don't know any Nicolino.

1015
01:04:43,916 --> 01:04:47,583
If Amalia doesn't want to...
She is the owner!

1016
01:04:47,791 --> 01:04:52,500
Don't cry,
don't make her cry. Poor girl!

1017
01:04:52,708 --> 01:04:57,041
This daughter
is making my existence bitter.

1018
01:04:59,125 --> 01:05:04,208
I went home so cheerful.
So happy.

1019
01:05:05,791 --> 01:05:10,666
You must stay like that Amelia.
Think about yourself.

1020
01:05:10,875 --> 01:05:12,708
Like I do.

1021
01:05:33,416 --> 01:05:36,000
I don't want to keep closed

1022
01:05:36,625 --> 01:05:40,000
these paper flowers.

1023
01:05:41,666 --> 01:05:45,333
The real flowers are blooming

1024
01:05:45,541 --> 01:05:48,875
in the garden for you.

1025
01:05:50,750 --> 01:05:54,125
Spring

1026
01:05:54,333 --> 01:05:56,833
is here!

1027
01:05:57,625 --> 01:06:01,916
Trees are becoming purple.

1028
01:06:03,958 --> 01:06:07,916
A bird is coming to say,

1029
01:06:09,083 --> 01:06:13,416
"I learned how to fly."

1030
01:06:16,541 --> 01:06:19,750
Years have passed.

1031
01:06:19,958 --> 01:06:23,000
Seasons are flying.

1032
01:06:23,208 --> 01:06:26,000
Songs are changing.

1033
01:06:26,208 --> 01:06:29,166
But not you, you are always the same.

1034
01:06:29,375 --> 01:06:32,625
For me you are still beautiful

1035
01:06:32,833 --> 01:06:35,416
because I love you.

1036
01:06:35,625 --> 01:06:40,916
The world is sad
if you don't laugh anymore.

1037
01:06:41,708 --> 01:06:44,083
Put some make up on.

1038
01:06:44,291 --> 01:06:47,375
Comb your hair.

1039
01:06:47,583 --> 01:06:50,916
Wear a brooch.

1040
01:06:51,125 --> 01:06:54,625
Come close to me.

1041
01:06:55,958 --> 01:06:59,208
This mirror

1042
01:06:59,416 --> 01:07:02,208
can do love miracles.

1043
01:07:02,416 --> 01:07:05,416
My heart still trembles

1044
01:07:05,625 --> 01:07:09,958
and falls in love with you.

1045
01:07:15,416 --> 01:07:18,000
Saint Gennaro, help Gaetanino.

1046
01:07:18,208 --> 01:07:20,333
Give him strength and courage.

1047
01:07:23,708 --> 01:07:26,083
What do you think, will he make it?

1048
01:07:26,291 --> 01:07:28,166
- No, no.
- No? I say yes!

1049
01:07:28,375 --> 01:07:31,041
- Yes.
- He will come and say:

1050
01:07:31,250 --> 01:07:33,750
Run to Carmelina,
she is waiting for you!

1051
01:07:33,958 --> 01:07:36,166
- I will go and kiss her.
- No!

1052
01:07:36,375 --> 01:07:38,583
No? Finally!

1053
01:07:39,625 --> 01:07:43,291
- So?
- I must talk to you.

1054
01:07:43,500 --> 01:07:46,458
- Did something bad happened?
- No, actually...

1055
01:07:46,666 --> 01:07:50,041
- It went well for me, but for you...
- What?

1056
01:07:51,250 --> 01:07:55,500
- Salam, go away.
- Me?

1057
01:08:02,500 --> 01:08:04,333
Speak.

1058
01:08:06,208 --> 01:08:09,083
Nicolino, you must be brave.

1059
01:08:10,083 --> 01:08:13,375
I can't let you marry Carmelina,
my new position forbids me.

1060
01:08:13,583 --> 01:08:15,916
What position?

1061
01:08:16,125 --> 01:08:20,041
Me and Amalia love each other
and we will get married.

1062
01:08:20,250 --> 01:08:24,125
- What?
- As Carmelina's father, I can't.

1063
01:08:24,333 --> 01:08:29,166
- Coward, traitor! What did you do?
- Calm down, Nicolino.

1064
01:08:29,375 --> 01:08:32,583
Why do you take it out on me?
It wasn't my fault if I fell in love.

1065
01:08:32,791 --> 01:08:35,583
If I am not getting married,
neither will you.

1066
01:08:35,791 --> 01:08:40,291
I will take the Turkish man
to Mrs. Amelia.

1067
01:08:40,500 --> 01:08:42,541
- Muzafer!
- If she finds out about that,

1068
01:08:42,750 --> 01:08:44,750
it would be bad for you too.

1069
01:08:46,541 --> 01:08:48,583
Oh, man! I lost the Turkish man.

1070
01:08:49,500 --> 01:08:52,541
Gaetanino!
Help me, I lost the Turkish man.

1071
01:08:52,750 --> 01:08:55,916
I don't care, I am going.
Amelia is waiting for me.

1072
01:08:56,125 --> 01:08:58,250
Muzafer! Muzafer!

1073
01:09:04,916 --> 01:09:08,541
Are you looking for the Turkish man?
He is on the terrace.

1074
01:09:08,750 --> 01:09:10,541
- Muzafer!
- He got crazy!

1075
01:09:23,875 --> 01:09:27,208
- What are you doing?
- I am praying Allah. Pray as well.

1076
01:09:27,416 --> 01:09:29,250
Let's go.

1077
01:09:32,083 --> 01:09:35,583
Wait! Here lives GiosuÃ¨'s wife.
The Gerace family.

1078
01:09:35,791 --> 01:09:38,958
- You said that everybody died.
- I will explain later. Let's go!

1079
01:09:39,166 --> 01:09:42,250
I understand.
We are going to the funeral.

1080
01:09:42,458 --> 01:09:47,333
I know someone
who deserves a funeral.

1081
01:09:48,458 --> 01:09:50,375
What happened to you?

1082
01:09:50,583 --> 01:09:53,125
Carmelina thought
that you committed suicide.

1083
01:09:53,333 --> 01:09:56,250
Another Turkish man!
There was a landing?

1084
01:09:56,458 --> 01:09:58,541
I'll tell you later.
Is Carmelina home?

1085
01:09:58,750 --> 01:10:01,583
- She is doing laundry.
- Alone?

1086
01:10:01,791 --> 01:10:06,416
Yes, alone.
Amalia lives in Turkey now!

1087
01:10:06,958 --> 01:10:09,291
I will take her with me,
I'll kidnap her.

1088
01:10:09,500 --> 01:10:12,125
- Take care of him.
- No, I am afraid!

1089
01:10:12,333 --> 01:10:14,583
It's very good. I'll be back soon.

1090
01:10:14,791 --> 01:10:18,541
- Are you going to the funeral?
- Funeral?

1091
01:10:18,750 --> 01:10:23,541
- What funeral?
- You are ignorant.

1092
01:10:23,750 --> 01:10:26,166
- No, you are dumb!
- Me?

1093
01:10:26,375 --> 01:10:28,375
Yes, you are dumb.

1094
01:10:33,500 --> 01:10:35,541
Carmelina!

1095
01:10:35,750 --> 01:10:38,083
Carmelina, I am here!

1096
01:10:39,166 --> 01:10:43,166
Nicolino! How did you find out
that I was here alone?

1097
01:10:43,375 --> 01:10:46,750
I live thinking about you.

1098
01:10:46,958 --> 01:10:50,416
Are you really alone?

1099
01:10:50,625 --> 01:10:53,041
Yes, mom is downstairs.

1100
01:10:54,083 --> 01:10:56,000
I can't believe...

1101
01:10:56,208 --> 01:10:59,666
We are here alone.

1102
01:10:59,875 --> 01:11:04,416
- It's the first time.
- I know, but what is this for?

1103
01:11:05,875 --> 01:11:08,166
- Can I help you?
- Thank you.

1104
01:11:24,875 --> 01:11:27,208
I can't see you but I feel you.

1105
01:11:32,833 --> 01:11:35,541
Should I come to the other side?

1106
01:11:40,791 --> 01:11:43,291
You have nothing to say?

1107
01:11:47,791 --> 01:11:50,666
- Carmelina!
- What do you want?

1108
01:11:50,875 --> 01:11:54,416
- Don't dare come closer.
- And I will come closer anyway.

1109
01:11:54,625 --> 01:11:58,083
We are not even engaged.

1110
01:11:58,291 --> 01:12:02,458
Carmelina, what are we?
I still have to understand that!

1111
01:12:02,666 --> 01:12:06,625
We are engaged every other month.
Parents of a child who doesn't exist.

1112
01:12:06,833 --> 01:12:09,708
In love without even
being able to say it.

1113
01:12:09,916 --> 01:12:13,833
Now that we are finally alone,
you don't want me to get closer.

1114
01:12:14,041 --> 01:12:18,000
I'm coming closer, Carmelina.
Don't you say a word?

1115
01:12:18,208 --> 01:12:21,708
Careful, Nicolino.
You can ruin me.

1116
01:12:21,916 --> 01:12:23,833
Run away, then!

1117
01:12:25,666 --> 01:12:29,416
- Of course I will run away!
- Wait, I must tell you something.

1118
01:12:29,625 --> 01:12:32,625
I could never do it
and I don't know if I will now.

1119
01:12:34,916 --> 01:12:38,583
- Should I tell you, Carmelina?
- What? Are you crazy?

1120
01:12:38,791 --> 01:12:41,041
No, but I will get crazy.

1121
01:12:42,833 --> 01:12:45,708
Aren't you running away?
Carmelina, aren't you?

1122
01:12:46,458 --> 01:12:48,500
I'm running away.

1123
01:12:48,708 --> 01:12:52,166
Carmelina, I...
Damn, it is so difficult!

1124
01:12:53,041 --> 01:12:55,500
I care for you.

1125
01:12:55,708 --> 01:12:58,916
Nicolino, I didn't hear you.

1126
01:12:59,125 --> 01:13:01,166
I care for you.

1127
01:13:02,916 --> 01:13:04,791
I care for you!

1128
01:13:05,000 --> 01:13:07,583
See, how beautiful is this word?

1129
01:13:07,791 --> 01:13:10,541
I care for you!

1130
01:13:11,333 --> 01:13:13,458
There is no one here?

1131
01:13:13,666 --> 01:13:15,583
I care for you!

1132
01:13:15,791 --> 01:13:18,166
Carmelina. Am I crazy?

1133
01:13:18,375 --> 01:13:22,041
Nicolino, I am crazy.

1134
01:13:22,250 --> 01:13:24,041
I care for you.

1135
01:13:29,875 --> 01:13:32,416
Did you hear? It's you again!

1136
01:13:32,625 --> 01:13:35,708
You said that you wouldn't dirty
your hands with me.

1137
01:13:35,916 --> 01:13:38,416
No. In fact I will not.

1138
01:13:38,625 --> 01:13:42,416
Muzafer,
throw this person down the stairs.

1139
01:13:43,416 --> 01:13:46,791
Gaetano, don't move. Downstairs
there is the real Turkish man!

1140
01:13:47,000 --> 01:13:50,875
- He is ready to act.
- What are you talking about?

1141
01:13:51,083 --> 01:13:54,166
- Do you know each other?
- It is possible.

1142
01:13:54,375 --> 01:13:56,916
When you are at sea,
you meet lots of people.

1143
01:13:57,125 --> 01:14:01,458
What are you talking about?
You can't even swim!

1144
01:14:01,666 --> 01:14:03,958
He is not a sailor.

1145
01:14:04,166 --> 01:14:08,083
I sent him to your house
to have some help from the inside.

1146
01:14:08,291 --> 01:14:12,458
This is what you made me do
keeping me from seeing Carmelina.

1147
01:14:12,666 --> 01:14:16,625
- Who are you, then?
- I will tell you who he is.

1148
01:14:16,833 --> 01:14:20,916
He is a rascal, a puppet,
a betrayer of friendship

1149
01:14:21,125 --> 01:14:22,875
for a little bit of food!

1150
01:14:23,083 --> 01:14:26,333
Daddy's friend,
the only one who survived.

1151
01:14:26,541 --> 01:14:29,458
He never even
took the ferry to Capri.

1152
01:14:29,666 --> 01:14:34,166
Daddy's friend is downstairs.
I will go get him and bring him up.

1153
01:14:37,083 --> 01:14:41,875
- Listen, don't be vile!
- You'll pay for what you did to me.

1154
01:14:42,083 --> 01:14:45,500
- They will kill each other!
- Don't move.

1155
01:14:53,333 --> 01:14:56,458
Now you also know

1156
01:14:56,666 --> 01:14:59,666
what it means to be in love.

1157
01:14:59,875 --> 01:15:02,833
They didn't die. You are bringing
bad luck to this building.

1158
01:15:03,041 --> 01:15:06,291
We will need lots of incense. Go!

1159
01:15:06,500 --> 01:15:08,583
- Go!
- You ruined me!

1160
01:15:08,791 --> 01:15:11,916
- After all that I did for you!
- I will make you go on a boat.

1161
01:15:12,125 --> 01:15:14,333
- But on an hospital boat!
- Gaetano!

1162
01:15:14,541 --> 01:15:18,166
- I will send you to the hospital.
- Nicolino! Gaetano!

1163
01:15:18,375 --> 01:15:21,041
Miss, come here.

1164
01:15:21,250 --> 01:15:24,833
- Is she Mrs. Gerace?
- There she is.

1165
01:15:25,041 --> 01:15:27,791
This is another Turkish man.
He says that you were dead.

1166
01:15:33,458 --> 01:15:35,041
Who are you?

1167
01:15:40,583 --> 01:15:44,208
Are you slapping me?
I am your best friend!

1168
01:15:47,833 --> 01:15:52,750
And you treat me like that
after all that I did for you?

1169
01:15:55,416 --> 01:15:57,250
Nicolino...

1170
01:15:58,125 --> 01:16:00,333
We grew up together!

1171
01:16:03,666 --> 01:16:08,000
You knew that I was in love!

1172
01:16:14,583 --> 01:16:16,916
It's not my fault if I fell in love too!

1173
01:16:23,041 --> 01:16:24,916
Gaetanino...

1174
01:16:25,125 --> 01:16:29,166
- Are you in love for real?
- Yes.

1175
01:16:30,208 --> 01:16:33,041
Come here, Gaetanino.

1176
01:16:33,250 --> 01:16:35,666
Come here!

1177
01:16:40,333 --> 01:16:44,250
You aren't dead!
You're alive. I don't understand.

1178
01:16:44,458 --> 01:16:48,666
You understand very well!
I am dead, dead!

1179
01:16:48,875 --> 01:16:52,416
I don't want to hear again about
GiosuÃ¨, Turkish men and ships.

1180
01:16:52,625 --> 01:16:55,500
Don't you bother me anymore.

1181
01:16:55,708 --> 01:17:00,375
- We don't accept visits anymore.
- I understood that!

1182
01:17:00,583 --> 01:17:03,708
She is not dead, she is alive.

1183
01:17:03,916 --> 01:17:07,416
Everybody tricked me,
poor Turkish man.

1184
01:17:07,958 --> 01:17:11,791
I will punish the guilty.

1185
01:17:13,000 --> 01:17:17,750
Good heavens! Gaetano, Nicolino...

1186
01:17:22,833 --> 01:17:25,291
So you will learn
not to make fun of me!

1187
01:17:26,416 --> 01:17:29,208
Amalia, Carmelina, come down!

1188
01:17:29,416 --> 01:17:32,375
The Turkish man is beating them up.

1189
01:17:35,208 --> 01:17:37,333
Mrs. Annunziata!

1190
01:17:37,541 --> 01:17:40,500
The Turkish man is beating up
Gaetano and Nicolino.

1191
01:17:40,708 --> 01:17:44,500
- What is going on?
- Thank God! Someone is coming up.

1192
01:17:45,875 --> 01:17:47,666
Nicolino?

1193
01:17:48,541 --> 01:17:50,375
What did you do to him?

1194
01:17:57,833 --> 01:18:02,041
My Nicolino! Are you alive?
What did they do to you?

1195
01:18:02,250 --> 01:18:05,000
I don't know.

1196
01:18:05,208 --> 01:18:08,291
Send him away.
I don't want to see him anymore.

1197
01:18:10,583 --> 01:18:14,583
- Amalia, forgive me.
- After all, he did it for love!

1198
01:18:14,791 --> 01:18:16,791
I care for you.

1199
01:18:28,791 --> 01:18:31,208
Nicolino, I care for you.

1200
01:18:43,708 --> 01:18:47,083
Nicolino, I have decided.
I will say it in front of everybody!

1201
01:18:47,291 --> 01:18:50,833
- I will run away with you!
- No.

1202
01:18:51,041 --> 01:18:55,125
Are you coming by yourself
or with your mother?

1203
01:19:00,250 --> 01:19:03,000
Carmelina, be good. I'm your mother.

1204
01:19:03,208 --> 01:19:05,375
Come upstairs and bring Nicolino too.

1205
01:19:05,583 --> 01:19:07,750
Nicolino, obey. It's better for you.

1206
01:19:07,958 --> 01:19:11,541
Obey, Nicolino.
I fixed everything for you too.

1207
01:19:14,000 --> 01:19:17,583
Amelia, a little bit of patience.

1208
01:19:24,708 --> 01:19:28,125
Poor mom, maybe I shouldn't do it.

1209
01:19:31,250 --> 01:19:33,083
Let's make an experiment.

1210
01:19:37,125 --> 01:19:40,750
Pretty girl, come upstairs
because I have to forgive you.

1211
01:19:40,958 --> 01:19:44,541
Nicolino, come upstairs.
We have already forgiven you!

1212
01:19:44,750 --> 01:19:48,333
I am your father,
we are getting married!

1213
01:19:55,333 --> 01:19:57,125
Young man!

1214
01:19:58,333 --> 01:20:01,125
You can't kiss in the street.

1215
01:20:02,166 --> 01:20:04,666
- Did you see everything?
- Everything.

1216
01:20:04,875 --> 01:20:08,291
Then fine us,
do whatever you want.

1217
01:20:08,500 --> 01:20:10,500
I want you as my best man.

1218
01:20:22,583 --> 01:20:26,208
Amalia, now that our children
have left happily,

1219
01:20:26,416 --> 01:20:30,916
let's take care of our happiness.
I am in a hurry!

1220
01:20:31,125 --> 01:20:34,875
I am so confused.
How can I say no to you?

1221
01:20:35,083 --> 01:20:39,708
Muzafer, Gaetanino,
you must calm down.

1222
01:20:39,916 --> 01:20:43,916
Did you ask permission
to your mother?

1223
01:20:46,625 --> 01:20:48,833
Do you have a mother as well?

1224
01:20:51,166 --> 01:20:56,208
Come closer.
What are you doing there standing?

1225
01:20:56,416 --> 01:21:00,166
Why did you come visit me?

1226
01:21:00,375 --> 01:21:02,250
Mom, I told you already.

1227
01:21:02,458 --> 01:21:05,208
We came to discuss
with you our wedding.

1228
01:21:05,416 --> 01:21:08,166
Wedding? Who is the groom?

1229
01:21:10,250 --> 01:21:12,958
- Me, mom!
- Mom?

1230
01:21:13,166 --> 01:21:15,916
When did I have you?

1231
01:21:16,125 --> 01:21:19,583
He is calling you "mom"
because he is the groom.

1232
01:21:19,791 --> 01:21:22,833
He is the groom and this is why
he is calling me "mom".

1233
01:21:23,041 --> 01:21:26,000
Come forward, sit and talk to me.

1234
01:21:27,750 --> 01:21:29,666
Go.

1235
01:21:32,791 --> 01:21:35,208
Come closer. He is shy!

1236
01:21:37,583 --> 01:21:40,333
You look like an angel.

1237
01:21:40,541 --> 01:21:42,916
You are so curly!

1238
01:21:43,916 --> 01:21:45,750
- What is your name?
- Gaetano.

1239
01:21:45,958 --> 01:21:47,750
Gaetano. What a nice name!

1240
01:21:47,958 --> 01:21:49,875
How old are you?

1241
01:21:50,083 --> 01:21:53,916
- 34.
- 34? What a nice age!

1242
01:21:54,125 --> 01:21:57,083
- What is your job?
- I am a...

1243
01:21:57,291 --> 01:22:00,333
- Knife grinder? I don't like it.
- No!

1244
01:22:00,541 --> 01:22:03,208
- I'm a projector.
- A projector?

1245
01:22:03,416 --> 01:22:05,458
Film projector.

1246
01:22:05,666 --> 01:22:08,666
- Film...
- I work at the movie theater.

1247
01:22:08,875 --> 01:22:12,291
How long have you been dating?

1248
01:22:13,500 --> 01:22:16,500
- It has been almost 20 days.
- 20 days?

1249
01:22:16,708 --> 01:22:19,541
Like cats? And do you call this love?

1250
01:22:19,750 --> 01:22:23,125
- It's terrible!
- I love him, mom!

1251
01:22:23,333 --> 01:22:25,166
What mom and mom!

1252
01:22:25,375 --> 01:22:28,583
The mother of the mother
of the first mother of my mother

1253
01:22:28,791 --> 01:22:30,958
used to say that to know a man well

1254
01:22:31,166 --> 01:22:34,125
you must use seven barrels of salt.

1255
01:22:34,333 --> 01:22:39,250
You must know each other,
get to know each other well.

1256
01:22:39,458 --> 01:22:42,958
You need time.
Three years is my verdict.

1257
01:22:44,583 --> 01:22:46,833
Here we go again!

1258
01:22:47,041 --> 01:22:52,458
You, your mom, and I
walking around Toledo.

1259
01:22:52,666 --> 01:22:56,458
We walk ahead
and your mother walks behind us.

1260
01:22:56,666 --> 01:22:59,708
You, your mom, and I.
I am in trouble!

1261
01:22:59,916 --> 01:23:02,541
You, your mom, and I.
Who'd make me do?

1262
01:23:02,750 --> 01:23:07,166
You, your mom, and I.
What a sin did I do?

1263
01:23:07,375 --> 01:23:10,166
You, your mom, and I.
